  ## Architecture Constraints
  - **Auth chain**: OAuth → GEMINI_API_KEY → ~/.gemini/.env (match utils/embedding.ts)
  - **DB pool**: Use shared `getPool()` from utils/db.ts (NEVER new Pool())
  - **Redis**: Use shared `getRedis()` from utils/redis.ts (NEVER new Redis())
  - **Embeddings**: Use shared `generateEmbedding()` from utils/embedding.ts
  - **Embeddings**: Use shared `generateEmbedding()` from utils/embedding.ts
  - **MCP tools**: Register new tools in tool-registry.ts with proper Zod schemas (use z.any() NOT z.unknown())
  - **ESM**: All imports use `.js` extension (TypeScript ESM)
  - **No circular deps**: Task 16 specifically warns — use raw SQL in memory.ts, don't import contradictions.ts
  - **Exit handlers**: Only utils/db.ts and utils/redis.ts own process cleanup
